data.description: Impressive Aspen Floorplan .This beautiful 4BR/3.5BA home offers Smart Home Technology, key-less entry, & more! LVP flooring in Great room, foyer and kitchen. Owner's Suite on Main floor offers spacious closet, double vanities, separate shower, & garden tub. Spacious eat-in Kitchen w/ HUGE granite island & SS appliances open to Great Room with corner fireplace. Built-in cubbies off garage & across from laundry room. Two story entry foyer. Open Loft with huge storage closet upstairs. Jack n jill bathroom.t. Covered front porch. 10x10 Covered Patio out back. Privacy fence. 100% USDA Financing Eligible. Washer/dryer and Refrigerator to remain with the home.
